<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>٦٤٩٠ - حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/676">إِسْمَاعِيلُ </a>قَالَ: حَدَّثَنِي <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/5361">مَالِكٌ، </a>عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/3645">أَبِي الزِّنَادِ، </a>عَنِ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/3424">الْأَعْرَجِ، </a>عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/3320">أَبِي هُرَيْرَةَ </a>عَنْ رَسُولِ اللهِ <span class="special">ﷺ</span> قَالَ: <span class="c2">«إِذَا نَظَرَ أَحَدُكُمْ إِلَى مَنْ فُضِّلَ عَلَيْهِ فِي الْمَالِ وَالْخَلْقِ،<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></span></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>⦗١٠٣⦘<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>فَلْيَنْظُرْ إِلَى مَنْ هُوَ أَسْفَلَ مِنْهُ.»<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>